{"tid":1605013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕人士有感","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T03:09:48.000Z","uid":272130,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0badf426171f4a4425c3098ad6cae092cd64021f","tid":1605013,"uid":272130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"難以珍容呢一刻的心情 相信好多香港人同我一樣 對於聽日有住好大既擔憂<br />\n對於個d 仲活係平行時空 仲飲飲食食緊既 你繼續啦 因為你是豬是改不了的性格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢支上簽 係我誠心幫香港求架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正如我之前講過我幫自己求支下下簽都靈驗左啦 天佑香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港雖然細 雖然人少 但我地造就左世界10 大城市既GDP 我地可以同倫敦 紐約齊名 因為d 咩？ 因為香港人真係好叻呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地一定要對準政權 呢個政府破壞左我屋企呀 我好x 嬲呀 我同自己講我要用一世既氣力要佢地還呀 唔好質問我可以做d 咩 有d 咩我可以做到我都會做 當初6.12 我第二日已經講左要告一哥 佢開槍打我daddy 係咪唔洗還呀dllm ?! 我唔會忍我一定要告 有人質疑我一個咩都無既女仔點告 我而家做到啦籌到6M 仲有好多人等緊捐款支持我地告黑警呀！！！！！ 我做到啦 我唔會妄自菲薄 因為只要相信 無野做唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你愈要打壓我地 愈要出黎 驚？你而家仲可以驚 之後你覺得你仲可以驚咩 仲有我希望身邊朋友做得幾多得幾多 捐錢/物資支援（衫呀車票呀揸車呀）/仲有就係好重要街坊支援（著靚靚OL 裝零gear 見到有年青人要幫手幫佢地buy time 呀！好重要呀） 扮跌低扮執野扮搵隱形眼鏡各位發揮演技啦 我地其實人好多架 對方3 萬再外加1 萬黑社會藍屍 我地係200 萬人 就算減左被拉既2000人 我都仲有199萬零8000 人呀 做得幾多就做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2000 人被拉 相信佢可以搵到5000甚至1萬人 日後支援好重要 做老闆既幫手請番佢呢d 被捕人士 佢地可以企出黎因為香港未來而送上自己前程 你係咪可以優先考慮請番佢地呀 當中有不少被捕人士真係因為救人而被拉 我知道我真係知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港只能自己救 外國勢力只能幫我地一把 勿以善小而不為 我既朋友仔 至少我可以好肯定講我屋企因為香港付出不少 我唔要大家既錢呀 我想大家行出黎撐大家 唔好令我失望 唔好令我有被遺棄既感覺 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位 江湖見 有一日 煲底見。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ycz5bFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcz5bFR.jpg&h=9703e225&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d7150b2d49027a93c31ea45d8e89821c32b6cf7","tid":1605013,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0b2266a72d402489ae2df73388d2c45827b736","tid":1605013,"uid":272130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0db1b9524d657f42b310a3921cd91b8f3df4ce3","tid":1605013,"uid":303463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"我知道啦 應承你"},{"pid":"92fbf35c82e23ae2375790ec905c8ce419e3a636","tid":1605013,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d18d104685da6ac460f5b55151911019982da0cb","tid":1605013,"uid":267983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb6a488cfd58d102b9157620734dcb65db7cdb49","tid":1605013,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"絲打都比人拉左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1795a3d616e519f61ee8e14f7fcd4375662e95af","tid":1605013,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c9e6206d64918a073205770163c5b4e012486f","tid":1605013,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:08:19.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"ce80e7562d8fdbf9beae2b65e5e4a7a54abe2052","tid":1605013,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花要對準政權，梗係去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=13027b13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=e6cb5327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=60d0a3d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=e4e01b62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=1df0884a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=a3117982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"5f81787e4bd19f3b8897f7953f783b21d646fe4f","tid":1605013,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0badf426171f4a4425c3098ad6cae092cd64021f","tid":1605013,"uid":272130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime